import React from 'react';
import {
    Typography,
    Grid,
    Card,
    CardHeader,
    CardMedia,
    CardContent,
    CardActions,
    IconButton, 
} from '@material-ui/core';
import {
    ThumbUpAlt as Like,
    ThumbDown as Dislike,
} from '@material-ui/icons'
import './Home.css'


function Home() {
    return(
      <>
        <Grid container spacing={3} className="main">
            <Grid item xs={6}>
                <Card className="root">
                    <CardMedia
                        className="fotoFilme" 
                        image="./img/teste.jpg"
                    />
                    <CardContent>
                        <Typography variant="h5">Nome do Filme</Typography>
                        <Typography variant="subtitle1">
                            Descrição do filme
                        </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                    <CardActions disableSpacing>
                        <IconButton aria-label="Curtir">
                            <Like />
                        </IconButton>
                        <IconButton aria-label="Não gostei">
                            <Dislike />
                        </IconButton>
                    </CardActions>
                </Card>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </>  
    );
  }
  
  export default Home;
